\N<Rame>P-please... I'm begging you... Not here, not like this...

\N<Man>Heh, heh... What's wrong with that? I haven't been able to

The man who had fought with Rame in the training corps and
had been toying with her body until just a moment ago. After
the fight, he dragged Rame into an alleyway, indulging in

\N<Man>Heh heh... You were so cute earlier, Rame-chan...

\N<Rame>But that doesn't mean we should do this here... If someone

\N<Man>Heh heh... Ah, don't worry, no one's going to come here.

Ignoring Rame's confusion, the man began to strip off her

\N<Rame>Please... I'm begging you. We really could be seen by

\N<Man>So... right? Let's go to my place? I'll continue what we

The one who suddenly called out was Rozaro. He continued to

\N<Man>What do you mean 'what'? Can't you see? What are you even

\N<Man>Shut up! I won't take orders from you...!

\N<Rame>...

\N<Rozaro>Well then, what will it be? Shall we resort to force? I

\N<Man>Tch...! Remember this...!

\N<Rozaro>Hmph, such a cliché parting threat. If you're going to

\N<Rame>Um... Master... did you save me just now? Thank you so much.

\N<Rozaro>No need for thanks. You are an important friend of Riia's

\N<Ryuda Soldier>How is it, Lord Zuuteruka. Is this to say that the trial has

There was Irime, lost in the light of her eyes, not even

\N<Irime>Ah... ah! Mmm... mmm... ah.

\N<Zuuteruka>Yes, exactly. This is the essence of Mind Ryuda. This is

\N<Zuuteruka>The love between lovers, the friendship between friends, or
the bonds of family. All are fragile enough to be easily

\N<Zuuteruka>Especially a mother's love for her child surpasses those and

\N<Ryuda Soldier>...

\N<Zuuteruka>To the point where... it can freely change people's feelings

\N<Irime>Haah... mmm. Ah... fu... ah.

\N<Zuuteruka>But it's not just women who can enjoy this effect, right?

\N<Zuuteruka>With this, you can easily become stronger and save the

expand your dreams?
\N<Ryuda Soldier>Y-yes! We will follow Lord Zuuteruka wherever he goes...!
\N<Zuuteruka>Hehehe... what a bunch of opportunists.
